data_table.description: Sample ID, subject ID, and sample use variables obtained from participants with or without breast cancer and involved in the "GWAS in African Americans, Latinos and Japanese" project.

variable.name: SAMPID
variable.comment: Unique sample identifier; replicates will have the same SUBJID

variable.name: SUBJID
variable.comment: The same SUBJID may have two SAMPID (replicates)

variable.name: SAMPLE_USE
variable.value: SNP genotypes obtained using standard or custom microarrays
